{"search_data": "Jammu & KashmirJ&K Bank Sahafat Finance Scheme for Journalists in Jammu and Kashmir LaunchedJ&K Bank Sahafat Finance Scheme for JournalistsThe important features and highlights of this scheme are as follows:-J&K bank CEO and Chairman launches this scheme for journalists on 14 December 2017.Under this scheme, journalists can get easy loans from the bank.Subsequently, the minimum loan amount is Rs 50,000 and maximum loan amount is Rs 3,00,000.Accordingly, journalists can repay the maximum credit of Rs 3 lakhs in 60 EMIs.J&K Bank will provide this financial assistance as a term loan for buying cameras, laptops, tablets, books etc.Moreover, there is a cash credit facility for them to meet their basic routine requirements.Along with the Minimum Interest Rate, journalists will also get an insurance cover of Rs 4 Lakhs. For this, they will have to pay Rs 342 as an annual premium."}